{"tid":2234863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【片】現代嘅戰場上面士兵只不過係標靶","createTime":"2020-10-08T08:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T01:47:09.000Z","uid":65473,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2a78959206ebef97a3ce43a7fd07f915897519ea","tid":2234863,"uid":65473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T08:12:18.000Z","msg":"亞美尼亞同阿塞拜疆嘅戰爭片段裏面睇到，<br />\n人類嘅角色已經被無人機取代，<br />\n連同敵人對戰都稱唔上，<br />\n士兵係咪仲有存在必要？<br />\n上場嘅卒仔面對嘅只係無窮無盡嘅恐懼，<br />\n睇唔到嘅敵人，<br />\n不斷倒地嘅同伴，<br />\n同毫無預警嘅死亡。<br />\n人類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />戰爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CWLLPZ1gaZQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCWLLPZ1gaZQ&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5JriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=dd5fa602\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CWLLPZ1gaZQ</a>"},{"pid":"a7eb1adae805125cff2887add4632ecbcd94d5ef","tid":2234863,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T08:43:18.000Z","msg":"要用黑煙永久遮蓋太陽"},{"pid":"966635d78a0f368aa13c16dd83f23693be43131f","tid":2234863,"uid":65473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7eb1adae805125cff2887add4632ecbcd94d5ef","tid":2234863,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T08:43:18.000Z","msg":"要用黑煙永久遮蓋太陽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T08:51:12.000Z","msg":"遼寧號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526763d1caa2bcb0d00024cd6f9fb4096c47d846","tid":2234863,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"966635d78a0f368aa13c16dd83f23693be43131f","tid":2234863,"uid":65473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7eb1adae805125cff2887add4632ecbcd94d5ef","tid":2234863,"uid":11